"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:8.1.2\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">8.1.2</span> 标题：筏子（raft, float）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：דֹּבְרוֹת</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：dovroth)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:23\">1KI 5:23</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：σχεδία</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：schedia)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Wis14:5\">WIS 14:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Wis14:6\">WIS 14:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Esd5:53\">1ES 5:53</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0519_raft.jpg\" alt=\"一名男子在兽皮制成的充气木筏上捕鱼\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">一名男子在兽皮制成的充气木筏上捕鱼 (Austen Henry Layard, Nineveh and Babylon: a narrative of a second expedition to Assyria during the years 1849, 1850, and 1851, Public domain, via archive.org)</figcaption></figure>筏子是一种漂浮在水上的交通工具，将原木或木板并排绑在一起制成，也可以用充气的动物皮来制作，如下面的插图所示。筏子可以用来运输人或货物。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>虽然许多语言都有专门词语表示绑在一起做成筏子的原木，但翻译者应该避免使用专用术语。<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:23\">1KI 5:23</a> （《和》5:9）的中间部分可译为：“他们把原木扎在一起，让它们沿着海岸漂流”（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> 直译）。这里和<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Esd5:53\">1ES 5:53</a> 提到的筏子都不是运输工具，而是把原木从一个地方运送到另一个地方的方法。</p>\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Wis14:5\">WIS 14:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Wis14:6\">WIS 14:6</a> 中，希腊文<em>schedia</em> 一词有两种含义。第5节讲的是，人只需要一小块漂浮的木头，就能在大海上航行。第6节是回忆挪亚和他的家人（以及从他们而来的全人类）藉以得救的方舟。有些译本在两节经文中都使用了“筏子”（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New American Bible (1970)\">NAB</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Jerusalem Bible (1985)\">NJB</abbr> 直译）一词，因此对方舟的提指就比较模糊。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Jerusalem Bible (1985)\">NJB</abbr> 在第6节添加了一个脚注，表明该处是指挪亚方舟。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 的译法更好一点，在两节经文中都采用了“boat”（“船”）。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Wis14:1-Wis14:11\">WIS 14:1–WIS 14:11</a> 的段落标题是“比较木头偶像与挪亚木船”，这就表明整段经文都与挪亚方舟有关。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
